  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Approve Return & Generate JNT Resi",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"return_id\": \"PASTE_RETURN_ID_HERE\"\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/returns/approve",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "returns",
            "approve"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Approve return request dan auto-generate resi JNT via Biteship.\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Fetch return + order + user data\n2. Generate JNT shipment (origin=user, destination=toko)\n3. Update status to 'approved' + save waybill\n\n**Required:**\n- return_id: Valid UUID dari tabel returns\n- User address harus lengkap (alamat + kode pos)\n\n**Response:**\n- waybill: Nomor resi JNT\n- tracking_url: URL tracking JNT\n- pickup_address: Alamat user\n- destination: Alamat toko"
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "Success - Return Approved",
          "originalRequest": {
